<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-66-0974 </DOCNO><TEXT>Advanced controls were implemented on Ashland Oil's Reduced Crude Conversion(RCC) and Metals Removal System (MRS) units, the RCC and MRS main fractionatorsand the unit gas plant. This article describes the format used for theoperator documentation at Ashland. Also, a potential process unit problemis described which can be solved by good operator documentation. Thesituation presented in the paper is hypothetical, however,the type ofunit upset described an occur if proper precautions are not taken.</TEXT></DOC>